<title>Damlai Tuipi ah</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Damlai tuipi-ah ka thagau a vakvai,
 Gitloh gikpuo gimthei tak in;
 &quot;Ei hun zuonin&quot; ti a sapna aw nem chu zan,
 Lawngchawlhna mun chu ka tung tai.

[V2]
 Lawngchawlhna achun ka thagau a chawl tai,
 Tui-pi ah vaikit puong ka,
 Huihpi te nungin, tuipi kinawk mahleh,
 Isu-a chun ka bit zing hi.

[V3]
 2. Lungsieta ei hukdampa kawmah ki pie'n;
 A thu chu gingin ka um hi;
 Gitloh kawlbuh a kiei chawlhmun ka tungtai,
 Lawngchawlhna chu Lalpa ahi.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa, nei hihdam apat ka la deihpen,
 Isu chanchin hawih hi ahi;
 A nuom taphawt te d'in Hukdampa ahi,
 Lawngchawlhna a chawl nuomte din,

[V5]
 4. Hungin, Hukdampa kawmah, A hun ngak hi,
 Ama'n hun na hukdam ina;
 Lawngchawlhna ah na thagau hun pui inla,
 &quot;Ka nawpna pen ka tung tai&quot; ti'n.</lyrics>
</song>